description:
Have you ever wondered where this world is heading? Is there any place where we can find reliable information about the future, and is there anyone who we can really trust? 

Watch as Pastor Ted Wilson explores an amazing Bible prophecy that reveals both the past and the future! Through this Revelation of Hope episode, you will realize the reliability of the Bible and how much you, too, can put your trust in the God of the past, the present, and the future! 

Pastor Wilson is sharing Revelation of Hope directly from Indianapolis, IN.
